  <SourceScript>k__BackingField: 'IGM: Hey, I wanna start enchanting some of the
    furniture in my house.


    IGM: But apparently the only way to do that is to
    rub some magic ointment on it...


    IGM: Does magic ointment really exist...?
    Can you make it?'
